---
title: Green Pepper and Black Olive Flatbread with Chili Garlic Butter
description: If it’s pizza you’re craving, this fully-loaded flatbread is sure to satisfy. At the base, there’s a crispy crust ladled with Italian-spiced tomato sauce. On top, a bevvy of veggies: tender green pepper, briney black olives, and sweet, sliced shallot. Thought we forgot the cheese? Never. Melty, freshly-torn mozzarella takes center stage, giving you a cheese pull with every bite. After your creation emerges from the oven, don’t forget to drizzle with (or dunk into) homemade chili-garlic butter.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c798d95c445fa3dc7660122-89010316.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2019-w16-r8-green-pepper-and-black-olive-flatbread-5c798d95c445fa3dc7660122-06caaf1a.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/2019-w16-r8-green-pepper-and-black-olive-flatbread-5c798d95c445fa3dc7660122
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
